name: MaaS-www
body:
### Welcome to MaaS-API project
The purpose of the MaaS-IF project is to provide an open set of APIs for driving Mobility-as-a-Service ecosystem forward in a community fashion. The project documents the APIs and provides a reference implementation for anyone to use and integrate to.

### Authors and Contributors
Sami Pippuri (@pippuri)

Want to be included in this list? Give our maintainers a shout on how you can help!
